sta6
====

static site generator (bundler)

Installation
------------

Currently, you only install sta6 locally:

    git clone https://github.com/fwttnnn/sta6
  
Link the cloned repo into quicklisp registry:

    ln -s "$(pwd)/sta6" ~/quicklisp/local-projects

Documentation
-------------

The documentation for sta6 can be found in:

    sta6.vercel.app/
